songs.title: Wolves
songs.lyrics:
[Chorus]
The dogs keep barkin' when you sleep at night (Wassup)
The darkness creepin' when you close your blinds (Wassup)
The shit ain't leavin' when you close your eyes
It's all night (Ruff-ruff, ooh, ruff-ruff)
The dogs keep barkin' when you sleep at night (Wassup)
The darkness creepin' when you close your blinds (Wassup)
The shit ain't leavin' when you close your eyes
It's all night (Ruff-ruff, ooh, ruff-ruff)
